1
00:00:17,720 --> 00:00:19,440
What are you doing standing there?

2
00:00:20,440 --> 00:00:21,760
You scared me.

3
00:00:24,680 --> 00:00:27,600
What about you? What did you do?

4
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:33,240
What did I do?

5
00:00:41,240 --> 00:00:42,080
This.

6
00:00:54,840 --> 00:00:56,160
How did you know?

7
00:00:57,800 --> 00:00:59,840
You obviously messaged her.

8
00:01:00,480 --> 00:01:01,880
How could I not know?

9
00:01:04,600 --> 00:01:10,840
So… what did you do… to Ms. Nana?

10
00:01:20,360 --> 00:01:21,560
Are you angry?

11
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:25,960
Tell me…

12
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:28,040
what you did first.

13
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:30,680
So that I can decide…

14
00:01:31,720 --> 00:01:33,240
if I should be angry.

15
00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:44,280
So, what business do you have
with my boyfriend?

16
00:03:17,880 --> 00:03:20,120
