21
00:03:36,640 --> 00:03:40,160
Did Mr. Tharn send you to prank me?
He's gone too far, though.

22
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,640
Do I look like I'm pranking you?

23
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:46,080
Excuse me, this isn't funny anymore.

24
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:49,640
