so I let you handle it.

51
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:54,480
And you didn't let me down at all.

52
00:05:56,880 --> 00:05:57,760
What a jerk.

53
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:00,280
Or…

54
00:06:02,880 --> 00:06:04,200
