60
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:30,600
You're the only one I go soft on.

61
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:40,440
Come here.

62
00:06:40,520 --> 00:06:41,920
-What?
-Come on.

63
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:45,680
Smile.

64
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:46,840
-For what?
-Come on.

65
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:49,880
-Smile.
-No.

66
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:52,760
One, two, three!

67
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:09,120
I'M SORRY MY BOYFRIEND
REPLIED ON MY BEHALF.

68
00:07:16,200 --> 00:07:17,040
Good.

69
00:07:19,320 --> 00:07:20,320
