70
00:07:22,840 --> 00:07:24,200
I did good?

71
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:26,080
Yeah.

72
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:29,120
Since I did good…

73
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:34,400
