74
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:37,160
Let go. Let me go right now.

75
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,280
Let me go!

76
00:07:39,960 --> 00:07:43,240
In your dreams. You got me all worked up.

77
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:46,280
Come on, Type.

78
00:07:55,240 --> 00:08:02,040
MY WIFE IS CUTE, BRO.

79
00:08:05,400 --> 00:08:11,040
WHAT?

80
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:18,120
IT'S RARE TO SEE HIM GET JEALOUS.

81
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:29,400
Hey, I was just gone
for a minute to grab some food.

82
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:31,720
How come you've suddenly lost your mind?

83
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,920
Shut up, you slut.

84
