who always complains whenever we meet.

96
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:17,800
So I've got to be thick-skinned,
or else I couldn't survive.

97
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:20,800
So, why were you laughing?

98
00:09:21,880 --> 00:09:22,800
Tell me.

99
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:24,400
I'm paying attention.

100
00:09:25,520 --> 00:09:27,560
