that's called "being nosy".

101
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:32,960
Fine, I'm being nosy
because I know who you texted.

102
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:36,680
I wouldn't care if it wasn't someone
in the Khirikan family.

103
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:41,920
