209
00:17:18,160 --> 00:17:20,920
He doesn't care what's happening
around him at all.

210
00:17:22,280 --> 00:17:25,800
Then, wait till he gets out of his world
and ask again.

211
00:17:26,440 --> 00:17:30,840
