219
00:18:09,760 --> 00:18:11,080
Butt out.

220
00:18:16,800 --> 00:18:17,640
Eat.

221
00:18:23,440 --> 00:18:24,560
Eat.

222
00:18:26,560 --> 00:18:28,480
Let… go.

223
00:18:29,160 --> 00:18:30,320
Fiat.

224
00:18:32,960 --> 00:18:34,680
Okay, fine.

225
00:18:46,280 --> 00:18:48,320
