233
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:26,560
Damn! Wiener! Wiener! Wiener!

234
00:19:26,640 --> 00:19:30,440
That's enough. Stop joking. Eat.

235
00:19:31,680 --> 00:19:33,600
Leo, you're no fun.

236
00:19:33,680 --> 00:19:36,600
